🍋 When life gives you lemons, make (PINK!) Lemonade! 💕

#Lemonadeday

 - Recipe - 
🍋 Four lemons Plus one lemon for decorating 
🍓 1 lb of strawberries 
🍉 1/2 lb of watermelon 
5 cups of water 

Cut strawberries in half and add 2 cups of water into a blender 
Squeeze four lemons 
Add strawberries & watermelon 
Add honey or sugar to taste (optional) 
Add three more cups of water. 
Strain the lemonade to make it less frothy. 

Cool in the refrigerator for two hours before serving.
Oinktastic 🐽
